YOUR FALSE SENSE OF ENTITLEMENT IS IMPECCABLE. YOUR LEADERSHIP IS AS CLEAR AS FUCK AND YOUR BULLSHIT WILL ALWAYS BE BULLSHIT BECAUSE YOU'RE NOT CAPABLE OF ANYTHING! ANYTHING!

FUCK YOU AND YOUR STUPID WAYS.

Sincerely, JB
Life crashes like a wave, intoxicatingly traumatic.
One day, this pain will make sense to you.

Dear You,
Where have you been without me? Wait. Let me rephrase the question. Where have I been without you? THAT IS THE QUESTION!
I hope your conscience kills you. Love lots, Me

“When I come up against the real world, I just vacillate.”

-Robert Crumb

Dear You,

Love, 
ME

I'm so sick and tired of doing shit for other people. 

FUCK!
Akala ko ako lang ang hindi nakakaget-over kay ONDOY. Maraming tao pa pala.

the person who love you more will fight with you daily but whenever you are sad that person will fight with the world to end your sadness.


true story.
Getting older means getting bolder and wiser. Sana applicable Ito sa akin. Happy birthday to me!
"i love you" i proclaimed, into the air, to nobody, just to hear what it would sound like.
you met me at a very strange time in my life

When you said last night
that your goal in life
is to be the greatest mom
in the whole world,
my heart disintegrated 
and I cried inside. 

I love you.
There's some of me in you.
It happened to me. TRUE STORY!

Me? I don't care too much about the looks. I want an incisive, inquisitive, insightful, irreverent mind. I want someone for whom philosophical discussion is foreplay. I want someone who sometimes makes me go ouch due to their wit and evil sense of humor. I want someone that I can reach out and touch randomly. I want someone I can cuddle with. I decided this all means that I am sapiosexual.
Never judge anyone by their past. Life's all about new beginnings.

"You have to accept me for my shortcomings and understand that you're a better person than I am. I'm a little rotten. Please don't let that deter you though. Because when I look at you, I see someone who makes sense."

- I want to know you
(http://thoughtcatalog.com/2012/i-want-to-know-you/)

(fucking.accurate)

Hello Stranger!

Nice to hear from you again. Past still haunts you, eh? Ito lang ang masasabi ko:

It was a learning experience. Failur is cool. Sorry if you had to be the cavy! I am thankful with what I learned from you. Mas madami pa akong natutunan sa pagsasama natin kaysa sa school, libro, family, telebisyon, internet o sa kung ano mang nakakaimpluwensya sa akin. 


Love,

JBs

ps: At least, hindi ako magnanakaw! May your conscience and our past haunt you, forever.
Life right now is like high school again, minus the school uniform. I gotta find my own clique yo. fml.

i'm sorry i was not there on your special day. i'm sure you look beautiful tonight, as you were the other night when i saw you. (sigh) fuck work. what a kill joy. but hey, i found you... at work. so yeah. 

shet ang sakit ng ulo ko. 


ps. your smile makes me go lalalalalalalalah
